  "description": "A stunning nighttime view showcases a vibrant fireworks display over a cityscape and a long bridge extending across dark water. The fireworks explode in bursts of red, green, and white, illuminating the sky above the urban landscape. Below, the city is aglow with countless lights, forming a dense pattern of buildings and structures. A prominent bridge, featuring lit support structures and cables, stretches horizontally across the frame. The water reflects some of the city lights and the colors of the fireworks, creating a shimmering effect. The composition is a long shot, emphasizing the scale of the city and the vastness of the night sky.",
